User stories:
1.	As a logged-out user, I want to be able to login.
2.	As a logged-in user, I want to see the list of to-dos I've previously created.  
3.	As a logged-in user, I want to see the financial breakdown of all my monthly subscriptions.
4.	As a logged-in user, I want to see the total amount subtracted from my bank account each month for subscriptions.
5.	As a logged-in user, I want to be able to cancel any of my subscriptions on the platform.
6.	As a user, I want to be reminded before a subscription is being renewed. 
7.	As a user, I want to be able to see the remaining time before a subscription renewal.
8.	As a user, I want to be able to see promotions offered on my subscriptions.
9.	As a user, I want to create lists of friends who share my subscriptions.
10.	As a user, I want to be able to register to new subscriptions using the platform.


wireframes - 
1.	Login view
2.	Search for a subscription to add to the account.
3.	The screen after you login - dashboard 


 
